OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome breaks
OL,6,Fin the cloud possible giving a
OL,7,Fbrighter end to the day, perhaps an
OL,8,Fisolated light shower. Cloud gradually
OL,9,Fincreasing towards dawn. Blustery
OL,10,Fwinds gradually easing through the
OL,11,Fevening, remaining lighter overnight.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FA chilly start under clearer
OL,14,Fskies but soon clouding over from the
OL,15,Fsouthwest. Turning increasingly windy
OL,16,Fas Storm Dave arrives with strong and
OL,17,Fgusty southwesterly winds developing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
