OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FBright
OL,6,Fbut blustery on Easter Sunday, with
OL,7,Fscattered showers. Winds easing
OL,8,Fleaving a drier, brighter, and warmer
OL,9,FEaster Monday. Settled on Tuesday with
OL,10,Fplenty of sunshine, with increasing
OL,11,Fcloud later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
